column5: Just curious if anyone has fished Anaharea lake. I've heard some good things about it, and am thinking of giving it a shot. Supposedly its a pretty nice trophy Pike/Lake Trout lake. Thanks!

I've been there four times. Last trip was 2013 and my group caught a couple 42" pike. My best was 39" and a few others were 36" plus. Good lake trout fishing. There are no walleye or bass in the lake. Let me know if you have questions.
